{{Top|leg}}
The '''Sunfire 1000''' was a [[Merr-Sonn Munitions, Inc./Legends|Merr-Sonn]] [[Flamethrower/Legends|flamethrower]] mounted in the belly of the [[Turbostorm-class gunship|''Turbostorm''-class gunship]].

==History==
These weapons were to put to good use by the [[Balawai]] militia on [[Haruun Kal/Legends|Haruun Kal]] during the [[Summertime War]], where they were used to clear the jungle and [[Korun/Legends|Korunnai]] positions with ease from the air.

